.IP "\fBint gpio_claim_alert(int sbc, int handle, int lFlags, int eFlags, int gpio, int nfyHandle)\fP"
.IP "" 4
This claims a GPIO to be used as a source of alerts on level changes.

.br

.br

.EX
      sbc: >= 0 (as returned by \fBrgpiod_start\fP).
